Formatting guidelines:
- Limit lines to ~80 characters --mhazinsk
- Use four-space indents, NOT tabs --mhazinsk

Potential future problems:
- The Peggy is limited to 14 kB of (compiled) flash memory -- can probably replace with ATMega644
- 16 MHz (?) CPU speed 
- No spare output pins -- all communications must be over serial, and the ethernet shield is not supported

Relevant documentation:
- http://www.evilmadscientist.com/article.php/PeggyArdLib 
